        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nas discussed lets stick to small moe dedicated test like so:\n\nquery for modules\n   a) 1 existing module\n   b) 2 existing modues\n   c) non-existing module name -> empty result\n\nquery for properties\n   a) 1 existing property name/value\n   b) 2 existing property name/values\n   c) existing property name but non existing value -> empty result\n   d) non-existing property name, value 'dont care' -> empty result\n\n\ncombined queries\n   a) existing module and property\n   b) non existing module + existing property -> empty result\n   c) existing module and non existing perty value -> empty result",
